# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Harness runtime state (ephemeral / 세션별 생성)
#   walwal-harness CLI 자체가 dogfooding 하면서 생성하는 파일들.
#   추적 대상은 gotchas/, HARNESS.md, config.json, archive/ 정도만.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────
.harness/progress.log
.harness/next-prompt.txt
.harness/actions/scan-result.json
.harness/actions/pipeline.json
.harness/actions/plan.md
.harness/actions/feature-list.json
.harness/actions/api-contract.json
.harness/actions/sprint-contract.md
.harness/actions/evaluation-*.md

